 longer used. You can delete it.'=>'此翻译新闻附加组件已迁移到主插件，不再使用。您可以删除它。','TranslatePress Add-ons'=>'翻译按增件','Translator Accounts'=>'翻译帐户','%1$sAdd-ons settings saved successfully%2$s'=>'%1$s已成功保存附加组件设置%2$s','Activate'=>'启用','Add-On'=>'扩展','Deactivate'=>'停用','Documentation'=>'文档','Do not automatically translate strings that are found in html nodes matching these selectors.<br>Excludes all the children of HTML nodes matching these selectors from being automatically translated.<br>Manual translation of these strings is still possible.'=>'不要自动翻译与这些选择器匹配的html节点中的字符串<br>排除自动翻译与这些选择器匹配的HTML节点的所有子节点<br>仍然可以手动翻译这些字符串。','Do not translate strings that are found in html nodes matching these selectors.<br>Excludes all the children of HTML nodes matching these selectors from being translated.<br>These strings cannot be translated manually nor automatically.'=>'不翻译匹配这些选择器的 HTML 节点中的字符串。<br>不翻译匹配这些选择器的 HTML 节点的所有子节点。<br>这些字符串既不能手动翻译，也不能自动翻译。','Exclude selectors only from automatic translation'=>'仅从自动翻译中排除选择器','Ads a slash at the end of the home_url() function'=>'在 home_url() 函数末尾添加斜杠','Force slash at end of home url:'=>'在主页 url 末尾强制斜线：','Detected long query limitation on WPEngine hosting. Some large pages may appear untranslated. You can remove limitation by adding the following to your site’s wp-config.php: define( \'WPE_GOVERNOR\', false ); '=>'检测到 WPEngine 托管的长查询限制。一些大型页面可能会出现未翻译的情况。您可以在网站的 wp-config.php 中添加以下内容来消除限制： define( \'WPE_GOVERNOR\', false )； ','If you can spare a few moments to rate it on WordPress.org it would help us a lot (and boost my motivation).'=>'如果您能抽出一些时间在 WordPress.org 上给它评分，那将对我们有很大帮助（并增强我的动力）。','No, thanks.'=>'不，谢谢。','Ok, I will gladly help!'=>'好的，我很乐意提供帮助！','Please enter your DeepL API key.'=>'请输入您的 API 密钥。','Please enter your Google Translate key.'=>'请输入您的 Google 翻译密钥。','Rate TranslatePress on WordPress.org plugin page'=>'在 WordPress.org 插件页面上评价 TranslatePress','There was an error on the server processing your Google Translate key.'=>'服务器在处理您的 Google 翻译密钥时出现错误。','There was an error with your Google Translate key.'=>'您的 Google 翻译密钥有误。','~ Razvan, developer of TranslatePress'=>'~ Razvan，TranslatePress 的开发者','Hello! Seems like you\'ve been using <strong>TranslatePress</strong> for a while now to translate your website. That\'s awesome! '=>'您好！看来您已经使用 <strong>TranslatePress</strong> 翻译您的网站有一段时间了。真不错！ ','TranslatePress Pro Add-ons'=>'TranslatePress 专业版附加组件','TranslatePress Pro Add-on'=>'TranslatePress 专业版附加组件','<strong>DeepL</strong> automatic translation is available as a <a href="%1$s" target="_blank" title="%2$s">%2$s</a>.'=>'<strong>DeepL</strong>自动翻译可以通过<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" title="%2$s">%2$s</a>启用。','Verbiage for the DeepL Pro Add-onTranslatePress Pro Add-on'=>'TranslatePress 专业版附加组件','TranslatePress'=>'TranslatePress','Translate Only Certain Paths'=>'仅翻译某些路径','Exclude Paths From Translation'=>'从翻译中排除路径','Choose what paths can be translated. Supports wildcard at the end of the path.<br>For example, to exclude https://example.com/some/path you can either use the rule /some/path/ or /some/*.<br>Enter each rule on it\'s own line. To exclude the home page use {{home}}.'=>'选择可以转换的路径。在路径末尾支持通配符。<br>例如，要排除https://example.com/some/path，可以使用规则 /some/path/ 或 /some/ *。<br>输入每个自己行。要排除主页，请使用{{home}}。','Do not translate certain paths'=>'不要翻译某些路径','Cleaning original meta table for language %s...'=>'为语言%s清理原始元数据表…','Regenerating original meta table for language %s...'=>'为语言%s重新生成原始元数据表…','The selected automatic translation engine does not provide support for these languages.<br>You can still manually translate pages in these languages using the Translation Editor.'=>'所选的自动翻译引擎不支持这些语言。<br>您仍可以使用翻译编辑器手动翻译页面为这些语言。','Unsupported languages'=>'不支持的语言','One or more languages are unsupported by the automatic translation provider. Please check the <strong>TranslatePress -> <a href="%s">Automatic Translation</a></strong> page for more information.'=>'自动翻译提供程序不支持一种或多种语言。详细信息 <strong>请查看翻译-> <a href="%s">自动翻译</a></strong> 页面。','Light'=>'明亮','Dark'=>'深色','Show the small "Powered by TranslatePress" label in the floater language switcher.'=>'在浮动器语言切换器中显示一个小小的"Powered by TranslatePress"标签。','Show "Powered by TranslatePress"'=>'显示 "Powered by TranslatePress"','Custom Language Flag'=>'自定义语言标志','Custom language'=>'自定义语言','Text RTL'=>'文本 RTL','Flag URL'=>'国旗URL','Native name'=>'母语名称','Language name'=>'语言名称','Select...'=>'选择...','Item name in quotes&ldquo; %s &rdquo;'=>'&ldquo; %s &rdquo;','Full Language Names No HTML'=>'完整语言名称 无 HTML','Customize the date formatting per each translated language.<br/>Leave empty for default WP setting or see more information <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/formatting-date-and-time/" title="Formatting Date and Time" target="_blank">here</a>'=>'为每种翻译语言设置自定义日期格式。<br/>留空使用WP默认设置，或<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/formatting-date-and-time/" title="Formatting Date and Time" target="_blank">在此</a>查看更多信息','Date format'=>'日期格式','Enable translation of numbers ( e.g. phone numbers)'=>'启用数字翻译（例如电话号码）','Translate numbers and numerals'=>'翻译数字和数字','Install & Activate'=>'安装并激活','Switch language to see the translation changes directly on the page.'=>'切换语言可直接在页面上查看翻译更改。','Don\'t forget to Save Translation. Use keyboard shortcut CTRL(⌘) + S'=>'不要忘了保存翻译，使用键盘快捷CTRL(⌘) + S','Quick Intro'=>'快速简介','Dismiss tooltip'=>'隐藏工具提示','Accept user payments, create subscription plans and restrict content on your membership site.'=>'接受用户付款, 创建订阅计划并限制您的会员网站上的内容.','Installing...'=>'正在安装…','A short list of plugins you can use to extend your website.'=>'可用于扩展网站的插件的简短列表。','Search for any text in this page in the dropdown.'=>'在此页面的下拉中搜索任意文字。','Capture more user information on the registration form with the help of Profile Builder\'s custom user profile fields and/or add an Email Confirmation process to verify your customers accounts.'=>'借助Profile Builder的自定义用户资料字段或添加电子邮件确认流程来验证您用户账户，在注册表单上获取更多用户信息。','Could not install. Try again from <a href="%s" >Plugins Dashboard.</a>'=>'无法安装。重试请通过 <a 