 are about to perform this action on all the strings matching your filter, not just the visibly checked. To perform the action only to the visible strings click "Select Visible" from the table header dropdown.'=>'您将要对与筛选器匹配的所有字符串执行此操作，而不仅仅是明显检查的字符串。若要仅对可见字符串执行该操作，请单击表标题下拉列表中的"选择可见"。','Select Visible'=>'选择可视','Select All'=>'全选','No strings match your query.'=>'没有与查询匹配的字符串。','Apply'=>'应用','See Less'=>'查看较少','See More'=>'查看更多','of'=>'的','items'=>'个项目','Import / Export'=>'导入/导出','Add New'=>'添加','Filter'=>'过滤','Edit'=>'编辑','Delete entries'=>'删除记录条目','Bulk Actions'=>'批量操作','Not translated'=>'未翻译','Automatically translated'=>'自动翻译','String Translation'=>'字符串翻译','Filter strings according to selected translation status, filters and keywords and selected filters'=>'根据所选翻译状态、筛选器和关键字以及所选筛选器筛选字符串','Search original strings containing typed keywords while also matching selected filters'=>'搜索包含键入关键字的原始字符串，同时匹配所选筛选器','You are about to perform this action only on the visible strings. To perform the action on all the strings matching the filter click "Select All" from the table header dropdown.'=>'您即将仅在可见字符串上执行此操作。若要对与筛选器匹配的所有字符串执行操作，请单击表标题下拉列表中的"全部选择"。','Dublin Core Description'=>'Dublin核心描述','Dublin Core Title'=>'Dublin核心标题','Miscellaneous options'=>'其他选项','Debug'=>'调试','Troubleshooting'=>'故障排除','Disable post container tags for post content'=>'禁用文章内容的文章容器标签','Disable post container tags for post title'=>'禁用文章标题的文章容器标签','It disables search indexing the post content in translated languages.<br/>Useful when the content of the post doesn\'t allow HTML thus breaking the page.'=>'此选项禁止搜索引擎索引此语言版本的文章内容。<br/>当文章内容不允许 HTML 从而破坏页面时非常有用。','It disables search indexing the post title in translated languages.<br/>Useful when the title of the post doesn\'t allow HTML thus breaking the page.'=>'此选项禁止搜索引擎索引此语言版本的文章标题。<br/>当文章标题不允许 HTML 从而破坏页面时非常有用。','Do not include translated links in sitemaps generated by SEO plugins.<br/>Requires <a href="https://translatepress.com/docs/addons/seo-pack/" title="TranslatePress Add-on SEO Pack documentation" target="_blank"> SEO Pack Add-on</a> to be installed and activated.'=>'不要在SEO插件生成的站点地图中包含翻译的链接。<br/>需要安装和激活<a href="https://translatepress.com/docs/addons/seo-pack/" title="TranslatePress Add-on SEO Pack documentation" target="_blank">SEO Pack Add-on</a>。','Exclude translated links from sitemap'=>'从站点地图中排除已翻译的链接','Plan C.'=>'计划 C.','Test it to see if everything is working. If something went wrong, you can restore the backup that you\'ve made at the first step. Check if no more errors occur while browsing your website in a translated language. Look at the timestamps of the errors to make sure you are not seeing the old errors. Only the most recent 5 errors are displayed.'=>'测试一下，看看是否一切都在工作。如果出现问题，您可以恢复第一步所做的备份。在以翻译的语言浏览您的网站时，检查是否不再出现任何错误。查看错误的时间戳，以确保您没有看到旧错误。仅显示最近的 5 个错误。','If your problem still isn\'t solved, try asking your hosting about your errors. The most common issue is missing permissions for the SQL user, such as the Create Tables permission.'=>'如果问题仍未解决，请就此错误咨询您的主机服务商。最常见的问题是 SQL 用户缺少权限，例如"创建表"权限。','Copy the relevant content from the duplicated tables (trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY for example) in the newly generated table (trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es) -- perform this step only if you want to keep the current translations'=>'从新生成的表 （trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY） 中的重复表（例如trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY）中复制相关 trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es内容 -- 仅当您想要保留当前翻译时，才执行此步骤','Remove the trouble tables by executing the DROP function on them'=>'通过执行故障表上的 DROP 函数来删除它们','Create a copy of each translation table where you encounter errors. You can copy the table within the same database (trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY for example) -- perform this step only if you want to keep the current translations'=>'在遇到错误时创建每个翻译表的副本。您可以在同一数据库中复制该表（例如，trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY）-仅在想要保留当前翻译的情况下执行此步骤','Create a backup of your database'=>'创建数据库备份','If your problem isn\'t solved, try the following steps:'=>'如果您的问题没有解决，请尝试以下步骤：','Plan B.'=>'计划 B.','Plan A.'=>'计划 A.','What you can do in this situation'=>'在这种情况下您可以做些什么','The SQL errors detected can occur for various reasons including missing tables, missing permissions for the SQL user to create tables or perform other operations, problems after site migration or changes to SQL server configuration.'=>'检测到的 SQL 错误可能出于各种原因发生，包括缺少表、SQL 用户缺少创建表或执行其他操作的权限、此问题一般出现在站点迁移后或更改 SQL 服务器配置后。','Go to Settings -> TranslatePress -> General tab and Save Settings. This will regenerate the tables using your current SQL server.'=>'转到设置->翻译->常规选项卡中并保存设置，此操作将在您的 SQL 服务器上重新生成数据表。','Go to Settings -> TranslatePress -> General tab and Save Settings. This will regenerate the tables using your current SQL settings. Check if no more errors occur while browsing your website in a translated language. Look at the timestamps of the errors to make sure you are not seeing the old errors. Only the most recent 5 errors are displayed.'=>'转到设置->翻译->常规选项卡中并保存设置，此操作将使用当前 SQL 设置重新生成表。使用已翻译的语言浏览网站，检查错误是否不再发生，查看错误的时间戳，以确保您没有看到旧错误，仅显示最新的 5 个错误。','Why are these errors occuring'=>'为什么会发生这些错误','These are the most recent 5 errors logged by TranslatePress:'=>'以下是TranslatePress记录的最新 5 个错误：','Logged errors'=>'记录的错误','If TranslatePress detects something wrong when executing queries on your database, it may disable the Automatic Translation feature in order to avoid any extra charging by Google/DeepL. Automatic Translation needs to be manually turned on, after you solve the issues.'=>'如果TranslatePress在数据库上执行查询时检测到错误，可能会禁用"自动翻译"功能，以避免 Google/DeepL 的任何额外费用。解决问题后，需要手动打开自动翻译。','Updating original string ids for language %s...'=>'正在更新语言%s的原始字符串 id ...','Cleaning original strings table for language %s...'=>'为语言%s清理原始元数据表…','Inserting original strings for language %s...'=>'插入语言%s的原始字符串…','Select languages'=>'选择语言','Select language'=>'选择语言','The content of this element should be written in the default language.'=>'此元素的内容应以默认语言编写。','This element will still be visible when you are translating your website through the Translation Editor.'=>'当您通过翻译编辑器翻译网站时，此元素仍将可见。','Choose from which languages to exclude this element.'=>'从中选择要排除此元素的语言。','Exclude this element from specific languages.'=>'从特定语言中排除此元素。','Exclude element from language'=>'从语言中排除元素','Choose in which language to show this element.'=>'选择显示此元素的语言。','Show this element only in one language.'=>'仅在一种语言中显示此元素。','Restrict element to language'=>'将元素限制为语言','Exclude from Language'=>'从语言中排除','Restrict by Language'=>'按语言限制','Please note that DeepL API usage is paid separately. See <a href="https://www.deepl.com/pro.html#developer">DeepL pricing information</a>.'=>'请注意，DeepL API 的使用是需要单独付费的。请参阅 <a href="https://www.deepl.com/pro.html#developer">DeepL 定价信息</a>。','TranslatePress Errors'=>'TranslatePress错误','There are no logged errors.'=>'没有记录的错误。','Automatic translation has been disabled.'=>'自动翻译已禁用。','<strong>TranslatePress</strong> encountered SQL errors. <a href="%s" title="View TranslatePress SQL Errors">Check out the errors</a>.'=>'<strong>TranslatePress</strong>遇到 SQL 错误。<a href="%s" title="View TranslatePress SQL Errors">查看错误</a>。','Enable the hreflang x-default tag for language:'=>'为语言启用 hreflang x-default 标记：','Enables the hreflang="x-default" for an entire language. See documentation for more details.'=>'启用所有语言的 hreflang="x-default"。有关详细信息，请参阅文档。','Use this HTTP Referrer if the API lets you restrict key usage from its Dashboard.'=>'如果API允许您在其仪表板中的限制密钥使用，请使用此 HTTP Referrer。','Only enable for testing purposes. Can impact performance.<br>All records are stored in the wp_trp_machine_translation_log database table. Use a plugin like <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-data-access/" target="_blank">WP Data Access</a> to browse the logs or directly from your database manager (PHPMyAdmin, etc.)'=>'仅为测试目的启用。<br>所有记录都存储在 wp_trp_machine_translation_log 数据库表中。使用<a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-data-access/" target="_blank">WP Data Access</a>等插件或直接从数据库管理员（PHPMyAdmin 等）浏览日志。','Enable Automatic Translation'=>'启用自动翻译','Automatically translate your website through the DeepL API.'=>'通过DeepL API自动翻译您的网站。','DeepL'=>'DeepL','Something went wrong, please try again.'=>'出错了，请重试。','Add a limit to the number of automatically translated characters so you can better budget your project.'=>'对自动翻译的字符数添加限制，以便更好地为项目编制预算。','Block Crawlers'=>'阻止爬虫','Test API credentials'=>'测试 API 凭据','By upgrading you\'ll get access to all paid add-ons, premium support and help fund the future development of TranslatePress.'=>'通过升级，您可以访问所有付费附加组件、高级支持，并帮助为TranslatePress的未来发展提供资金。','The daily quota for machine translation characters exceeded. Please check the <strong>TranslatePress -> <a href="%s">Automatic Translation</a></strong> page for more information.'=>'超过机器翻译字符的每日配额。有关详细信息， <strong>请查看翻译 <a href="%s">>-自动</a></strong> 翻译页面。','Automatic Translation'=>'自动翻译','Do not automatically translate these strings (ex. names, technical words...)<br>Paragraphs containing these strings will still be translated except for the specified part.'=>'不要自动翻译这些字符串（例如名称、技术词...）<br>包含这些字符串的段落仍将翻译，但指定的部分除外。','Exclude strings from automatic translation'=>'从自动转换中排除字符串','String'=>'字符串','Limit machine translation / characters per day'=>'限制机器翻译每天的字符数','Log machine translation queries.'=>'记录机器翻译查询。','Top Left'=>'左上','Top Right'=>'右上','Bottom Left'=>'左下角','Bottom Right'=>'右下角','Fix missing dynamic content'=>'修复缺少的动态内容','Exclude selectors from translation'=>'从翻译中排除选择器','May help fix missing content inserted using JavaScript. <br> It shows dynamically inserted content in original language for a moment before the translation request is finished.'=>'可能有助于修复使用 JavaScript 插入的缺失内容。 <br> 在翻译请求完成之前，它会以原始语言动态显示插入的内容。','Exclude these strings from being translated as Gettext strings by TranslatePress. Leave the domain empty to take into account any Gettext string.<br/>Can still be translated through po/mo files.'=>'排除这些字符串，使其不被TranslatePress翻译为Gettext字符串，留空此项可翻译所有 Gettext 字符串。<br/>您仍可以通过 po/mo 文件进行翻译。','Experience a better way of translating your WordPress site using a visual front-end translation editor, with full support for WooCommerce and site builders.'=>'使用前端可视化编辑器翻译网站，体验翻译WordPres网站的更好方式，完全支持WooCommerce和页面生成工具。','Click to Copy'=>'点击复制','Suggestions from translation memory'=>'来自翻译记忆库的建议','No available suggestions'=>'没有可用的建议','Settings saved.'=>'设置已保存。','IMPORTANT: It is strongly recommended to first backup the database!! Are you sure you want to continue?'=>'重要提示：强烈建议您先备份数据库！确实要继续吗？','IMPORTANT: It is strongly recommended to first backup the database!
Are you sure you want to continue?'=>'重要提示：强烈建议您先备份数据库！
确实要继续吗？','Are you sure you want to remove this item?'=>'确定要删除此项吗?','Advanced'=>'高级','Filter Gettext wrapping from post meta'=>'从文章元数据中过滤Gettext包裹','Filter Gettext wrapping from post content and title'=>'从文章内容和标题中过滤 Gettext 包裹','Exclude from dynamic translation'=>'从动态翻译中排除','Selector'=>'选择器','Fix broken HTML'=>'修复损坏的 HTML','Exclude Gettext Strings'=>'排除Gettext字符串','Domain'=>'域名','Filters gettext wrapping such as #!trpst#trp-gettext from all updated post content and post title. Does not affect previous post content. <br/><strong>Database backup is recommended before switching on.</strong>'=>'从所有更新后的文章标题和内容中过滤gettext换行，如 #!trpst#trp-gettext，此操作不影响以前的文章内容。<br/><strong>建议在打开之前备份数据库。</strong>','Do not dynamically translate strings that are found in html nodes matching these selectors.<br>Excludes all the children of HTML nodes matching these selectors from being translated using JavaScript.<br/>These strings will still be translated on the server side if possible.'=>'不要动态转换在与这些选择器匹配的html节点中找到的字符串。<br>排除与这些选择器匹配的所有HTML节点的子级，不使用JavaScript进行转换。<br/>如果可能，仍在服务器端转换这些字符串。','Filters gettext wrapping such as #!trpst#trp-gettext from all updated post meta. Does not affect previous post meta. <br/><strong>Database backup is recommended before switching on.</strong>'=>'从所有更新后的文章元数据中过滤gettext换行，如 #!trpst#trp-gettext，不影响上一个文章元数据。<br/><strong>建议在打开之前进行数据库备份。</strong>','Disable dynamic translation'=>'禁用动态翻译','It disables detection of strings displayed dynamically using JavaScript. <br/>Strings loaded via a server side AJAX call will still be translated.'=>'此项禁止使用JavaScript动态显示字符串的检测。<br/>通过服务器端Ajax调用加载的字符串仍将被翻译。','Automatically Translate Slugs'=>'自动翻译鼻涕虫','Add as many languages as you need for your project to go global. Publish your language only when all your translations are done.'=>'添加尽可能多的语言，您需要您的项目走向全球。只有在完成所有翻译后才发布您的语言。','Configure different menu items for different languages.'=>'为不同的语言配置不同的菜单项。','Use a subdirectory for the default language'=>'为默认语言使用子目录','Select the original language of your content.'=>'选择默认语言。','Dynamically Added Strings'=>'动态添加的字符串','Different Menu Items for each Language'=>'每种语言使用不同的菜单项','Publish only when translation is complete'=>'仅在翻译完成时发布','Are you sure you want to split this phrase into smaller parts?'=>'确实要将此短语拆分为较小的部分吗？','These addons extend your translation plugin and are available in the Business and Developer plans.'=>'这些附加组件扩展了您的翻译插件，并在商业计划和开发计划中提供。','These addons extend your translation plugin and are available in the Developer, Business and Personal plans.'=>'这些插件扩展了您的翻译插件，并在开发人员计划、商业计划和个人计划中提供。','Add a floating dropdown that follows the user on every page.'=>'在每一页上添加跟随用户的浮动下拉菜单。','Advanced Add-ons'=>'高级附加组件','Create translator accounts for new users or allow existing users that are not administrators to translate your website.'=>'为新用户创建翻译帐户，或允许不是管理员的现有用户翻译您的网站。','Navigate your website just like a particular user role would. Really useful for dynamic content or hidden content that appears for particular users.'=>'像特定用户角色一样浏览您的网站。对于显示给特定用户的动态内容或隐藏内容，非常有用。','Pro Add-ons'=>'专业附加组件','SEO support for page slug, page title, description and facebook and twitter social graph information. The HTML lang attribute is properly set.'=>'SEO 支持页面、页面标题、描述、脸谱和推特社交图表信息。HTML 朗属性设置正确。','Error! Duplicate URL slug values.'=>'错误！网址别名重复。','Back to TranslatePress Settings'=>'返回 TranslatePress 设置','Save changes to translation. Shortcut: CTRL(⌘) + S'=>'保存对翻译的更改。快捷键：CTRL（⌘）+ S','Saved'=>'已保存','Your HTTP referrer is: %s'=>'您的 HTTP referrer是： %s','Others'=>'其他','Images'=>'图片','Gettext Strings'=>'Gettext 字符串','Slugs'=>'别名','Strings that are user-created cannot be modified, only those from themes and plugins.'=>'无法修改用户创建的字符串，只能修改主题和插件中的字符串。','To translate slugs, please update the SEO Pack add-on to the latest version.'=>'要翻译别名，请将 SEO Pack add-on更新到最新版本。','This string is not ready for translation yet. <br>Try again in a moment...'=>'此字符串尚未准备好进行翻译。 <br>稍后再试...','Discard changes to this text box. To discard changes to all text boxes use shortcut: CTRL(⌘) + ALT + Z'=>'放弃对此文本框的更改。要放弃对所有文本框的更改，请使用快捷方式：CTRL（⌘） + ALT + Z','Discard all changes. Shortcut: CTRL(⌘) + ALT + Z'=>'放弃所有更改。快捷方式： Ctrl （⌘） + ALT + Z','Navigate to previous string in dropdown list. Shortcut: CTRL(⌘) + ALT + Left Arrow'=>'导航到下拉列表中的上一个字符串。快捷方式： CTRL（⌘） + ALT+ 左箭头','Navigate to next string in dropdown list. Shortcut: CTRL(⌘) + ALT + Right Arrow'=>'导航到下拉列表中的下一个字符串。快捷方式： CTRL（⌘）+ ALT+ 右箭头','Use this media'=>'使用这个媒体','Select or Upload Media'=>'选择或上传媒体','Add Media'=>'添加媒体','To'=>'到','From'=>'从','Close Editor'=>'关闭编辑器','Loading Strings...'=>'正在加载字符串...','Discard All'=>'全部舍弃','Saving translation...'=>'正在保存翻译...','Text'=>'文本','Submit attribute'=>'提交属性','Placeholder attribute'=>'占位符属性','Anchor link'=>'锚点链接','Title attribute'=>'标题属性','Alt attribute'=>'Alt属性','<strong>TranslatePress</strong> requires at least PHP version 5.6.20+ to run. It is the <a href="%s">minimum requirement of the latest WordPress version</a>. Please contact your server administrator to update your PHP version.'=>'<strong>TranslatePress</strong>至少需要PHP版本5.6.20+才能运行。这是<a href="%s">最新WordPress版本的最低要求</a>，请联系您的服务器管理员更新 PHP 版本。','For this option to work, please update the Browse as other role add-on to the latest version.'=>'要使此选项起作用，请将“作为其他角色浏览”附加组件更新到最新版本。','You have successfully activated your license'=>'您已成功激活许可证','You do not have permission to install plugin updates'=>'您无权安装插件更新','Error'=>'错误','There is a new version of %1$s available. %2$sView version %3$s details%4$s or %5$supdate now%6$s.'=>'新版本 %1$s 可用。 %2$s 查看版本 %3$s 详细信息 %4$s 或者 %5$s 现在更新 %6$s。','There is a new version of %1$s available. %2$sView version %3$s details%4$s.'=>'新版本 %1$s 已经准备好了， %2$s 查看版本 %3$s 详细信息 %4$s。','Your <strong>TranslatePress</strong> license will expire on %1$s. Please %2$sRenew Your Licence%3$s to continue receiving access to product downloads, automatic updates and support.'=>'您的 <strong>TranslatePress</strong> 许可证将在 %1$s内过期 。请%2$s续订您的%3$s许可证，以继续访问产品下载、自动更新和支持。','Your <strong>TranslatePress</strong> license has expired. <br/>Please %1$sRenew Your Licence%2$s to continue receiving access to product downloads, automatic updates and support. %3$sRenew now %4$s'=>'您的 <strong>TranslatePress</strong> 许可证已过期。 <br/>请 %1$s 续订您的 %2$s 许可证，以继续访问产品下载、自动更新和支持。 %3$s 立即续订 %4$s','Your license key has reached its activation limit.'=>'您的许可证密钥已达到其激活限制。','Your license key has been disabled.'=>'您的许可证密钥已被禁用。','Your license key expired on %s.'=>'你的许可证将期于%s过。','An error occurred, please try again.'=>'出现错误，请重试。','TranslatePress Database Updater'=>'TranslatePress数据库更新程序',' done.'=>' 完成。','Processing table for language %s...'=>'为语言%s处理数据表...','Updating database to version %s+'=>'将数据库更新为版本 %s+','Successfully updated database!'=>'已成功更新数据库！','Update aborted! Your user account doesn\'t have the capability to perform database updates.'=>'更新已中止！您的用户帐户无法执行数据库更新。','Update aborted! Incorrect action.'=>'更新已中止！操作不正确。','Update aborted! Incorrect language code.'=>'更新已中止！语言代码不正确。','Update aborted! Invalid nonce.'=>'更新已中止！无效的 nonce 。','We need to update your translations database to the latest version.'=>'我们需要将您的翻译数据库更新为最新版本。','Run the updater'=>'运行更新程序','TranslatePress data update'=>'TranslatePress数据更新','<strong>Warning:</strong> Some strings have possibly incorrectly encoded characters. This may result in breaking the queries, rendering the page untranslated in live mode. Consider revising the following strings or their method of outputting.'=>'<strong>警告：</strong> 某些字符串可能错误地编码了字符。这可能会导致中断查询，使页面在实时模式下未翻译。请考虑修改以下字符串或其输出方法。','Code'=>'代码','Visit <a href="https://cloud.google.com/docs/authentication/api-keys" target="_blank">this link</a> to see how you can set up an API key, <strong>control API costs</strong> and set HTTP referrer restrictions.'=>'点击<a href="https://cloud.google.com/docs/authentication/api-keys" target="_blank">这里</a>获取API key。<strong>控制API成本</strong>并设置HTTP referrer 限制。','Automatic User Language Detection'=>'自动用户语言检测','Translate by Browsing as User Role'=>'通过浏览翻译为用户角色','Extra Translation Features'=>'额外的翻译功能','Pro Features'=>'专业版功能','IMPORTANT: It is strongly recommended to first backup the database!\\nAre you sure you want to continue?'=>'重要提示：强烈建议您首先备份数据库！\\n确定要继续吗？','Done.'=>'完成。','&hellip;'=>'&hellip;','<strong>TranslatePress</strong> requires <strong><a href="http://php.net/manual/en/book.mbstring.php">Multibyte String PHP library</a></strong>. Please contact your server administrator to install it on your server.'=>'<strong>TranslatePress</strong>需要 <strong><a href="http://php.net/manual/en/book.mbstring.php">Multibyte String PHP 库</a></strong>才能工作，请联系您的服务器管理员安装。','Select how the language should be detected for first time visitors.<br>The visitor\'s last displayed language will be remembered through cookies.'=>'选择检测新访客语言的方法<br>，访客最后一次访问的语言将被记录在 Cookies 中。','WARNING. Cannot determine your language preference based on your current IP.<br>This is most likely because the website is on a local environment.'=>'警告。无法根据当前 IP 确定您的语言首选项。<br>这很可能是因为网站位于本地环境中。','Only by IP address'=>'仅按 IP 地址','Only by browser language'=>'仅按浏览器语言','First by IP address, then by browser language'=>'先按 IP 地址，然后按浏览器语言','First by browser language, then IP address (recommended)'=>'首先按浏览器语言，然后 IP 地址（推荐）','WARNING. Changing the default language will invalidate existing translations.'=>'警告。更改默认语言将使现有翻译无效。','replace the default flag'=>'替换默认标志','In most cases changing the default flag is all it is needed: '=>'在大多数情况下，需要更改默认标志： ','Even changing from en_US to en_GB, because they are treated as two different languages.'=>'即使从en_US 到 en_GB，因为它们被视为两种不同的语言。','Learn more in our documentation.'=>'请在我们的文档中了解更多信息。','Split block to translate strings individually'=>'拆分块以单独翻译字符串','Translate entire block element'=>'翻译整个块元素','Translate'=>'翻译','Save Changes'=>'保存更改','Language'=>'语言','https://translatepress.com/'=>'https://translatepress.com/','https://cozmoslabs.com/'=>'https://cozmoslabs.com/','All Languages'=>'所有语言','Default Language'=>'默认语言','Settings'=>'设置','Translator'=>'翻译者','Yes'=>'是','Coz